ğŸ“± Responsive Design (Very Important)

Tailwind uses **mobile-first breakpoints**.

| Prefix | Screen  |
| ------ | ------- |
| `sm:`  | â‰¥640px  |
| `md:`  | â‰¥768px  |
| `lg:`  | â‰¥1024px |
| `xl:`  | â‰¥1280px |

Example:

```html
<div class="text-sm md:text-lg lg:text-xl">
  Responsive Text
</div>
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ–±ï¸ Hover, Focus & States

```html
