  Hover Me
</button>
```

States:

* `hover:`
* `focus:`
* `active:`
* `disabled:`

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸï¸ Transitions & Animations

