------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ§  Customization (Config File)

Tailwind can be customized using `tailwind.config.js`.

```js
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      primary: '#1e40af',
    },
  },
}
```

