-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âŒ Common Tailwind Mistakes

* Very long class lists
* Not using responsive prefixes
* Ignoring reusable components
* Mixing Tailwind & CSS badly

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

* Use reusable components
* Use responsive utilities
* Keep class order readable
* Combine with frameworks (React, Next.js)

